WEBVTT

00:00:07.679 --> 00:00:10.361
The year is 1418.

00:00:11.412 --> 00:00:16.322
On the horizon, a shimmering vision
under the blazing sun.

00:00:17.151 --> 00:00:19.011
This is not a cloud,

00:00:19.011 --> 00:00:22.081
or anything you've ever seen before.

00:00:23.050 --> 00:00:25.776
It's an enormous ship

00:00:26.141 --> 00:00:29.632
followed by dozens and dozens more.